   <dc:description>
    <rdf:Alt>
     <rdf:li xml:lang="x-default">Explosion of bomb, rocket hit. Vector animation sprite sheet of burst with fire and black smoke clouds. Cartoon set of blast effect from dynamite, bomb or atomic weapon isolated on background</rdf:li>
